PROPOSED AMENDMENTS TO
SENATE BILL 1544
1 In line 2 of the printed bill, after “transportation” insert “; amending ORS
2 184.752”.
3 Delete lines 4 through 11 and insert:
4 “SECTION 1. ORS 184.752 is amended to read:
5 “184.752. As used in ORS 184.752 to 184.766:
6 “(1) ‘Public transportation service provider’ includes a qualified entity
7 and a city, county, special district, intergovernmental entity or any other
8 political subdivision or municipal or public corporation that provides public
9 transportation services and is not otherwise described in subsection (2) of
10 this section.
11 “(2) ‘Qualified entity’ means the following:
12 “(a)(A) Counties in which no part of a mass transit district or transpor-
13 tation district exists; or
14 “(B) Intergovernmental entities who are providing public transpor-
15 tation services on behalf of a county;
16 “(b) Mass transit districts organized under ORS 267.010 to 267.394;
17 “(c) Transportation districts organized under ORS 267.510 to 267.650; and
18 “(d)(A) Federally recognized Indian tribes; or
19 “(B) Intergovernmental entities who are providing public transpor-
20 tation services on behalf of a tribe.”.
